  {
    "Id": "165790",
    "ThreadId": "49540",
    "Html": "Apparently there is a property called rowstyle, so the answere is as fast as it is simple (thanks to google and a few found posts of others).<br>\r\nWith the code below the main issue of the OP is solved. All that remains now is when i uncheck the checkbox, the color of the row doesn't go back to its original color, but it will become a nasty shade of gray.<br>\r\nSo i can still use some help on that one.<br>\r\nCurrently i return null in the ConvertBack method. I did try to set the mode to oneWay on the background property, did not do any good.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnyway, here's the simple xaml which i found.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> ItemsSource</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=Employees}&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> AutoGenerateColumns</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;False&quot;&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid.Columns</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> IsReadOnly</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;True&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=Name}&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Header</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Naam&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> MinWidth</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;110&quot;&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridTextColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridCheckBoxColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> IsReadOnly</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;False&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Path</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=IsActive}&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Header</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Actief&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> MinWidth</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;50&quot;&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGridCheckBoxColumn</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid.Columns</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid.RowStyle</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> TargetType</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Type</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">DataGridRow</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">}&quot;&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Property</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Background&quot;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:13px\"><strong> </strong>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Value</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> IsActive</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Converter</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">={</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StaticResource</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> BackgroundColorConverter</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">},</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Mode</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=oneWay}&quot; /&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid.RowStyle</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">wpf</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">DataGrid</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMode=oneWay is'nt really necessary here. The name of the converter really should be something like BooleanToBackgroundConverter or something.<br>\r\n<br>\r\ngrtz,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMark\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
